citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:20pm on March 6,
2023. Knocked on facility door-no response. Called licensee leaving voicemail message and sent text message. License
responded by text message that he was unable to do an inspection today.
End Section
